name: APPROACH WITH CAUTION
description:
Friday. 6:00 PM.

The old kitchen radio crackles and beeps erratically.

A charismatic, friendly, but faded voice:

"Tonight's main headline: DOUBLE MURDER at Yoyogi Park!

This morning two heavily mutilated bodies ... adult males ...

*STATIC*

... discovered in Yoyogi Park...

*BEEP*

Victims unidentified ... so far ...

... 

Police are searching ... two young women ... 

... matching outfits ... 

...

... walking casually away from the scene ...  

several witnesses...

*STATIC*

... EXTREMELY DANGEROUS...... APPROACH WITH CAUTIO-"

The cobweb covered radio pops, abruptly losing power... 

And the blood soaked kitchen fades back into cold, silent, darkness.
